        "subject": "LU-957 scrub: osd-ldiskfs itable based iteration",
        "message": "LU-957 scrub: osd-ldiskfs itable based iteration\n\nBackport of commit: I3d80bb4a174d47429764e5cca35e4f07be52d50b.\n\nImplement inode table based object iteration in osd-ldiskfs.\nIt is implemented as DT iteration APIs, which can be used by\nup layer LFSCK to scan the whole device sequentially.\n\nSigned-off-by: Lai Siyao <laisiyao@whamcloud.com>\nSigned-off-by: Fan Yong <yong.fan@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: If128dc1930c1fed343ed63bef1a1c2d38aae28f2\n"
